    {
        "SurahNumber": 39,
        "AyahNumber": 13,
        "Tafseer": "\"Say, 'Indeed, I fear, if I should disobey my Lord, the punishment of a tremendous Day.'\" (13)\n\nThat is, tell them: 'I cannot violate the command I have received. If I should disobey my Lord, I fear the punishment of a highly severe Day. This same command has been given to you through me, and I have delivered it to you. If you are indifferent to your Lord's disobedience and the punishment of the Resurrection, do whatever you please. Neither can I hold your hand, nor am I responsible for your faith.'"
